dc_description_s: This data represents zoning in Bayfield County in 2022 and includes the layers 'BAYFIELD_AIRPORT_2022', 'BAYFIELD_GENERAL_2022' and 'BAYFIELD_SHORELAND_2022'.[Shoreland: This layer contains shoreland zoning data for Bayfield County. General:  Airport: This layer contains airport location data in Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/892/GIS-Data-Access]
